== Notable dropouts ==

* Isaias Afwerki abandoned his studies in 1966 and traveled to Kassala, Sudan to join the Eritrean Liberation Front.
* Meles Zenawi in 1975 left the university to join the Tigray People&#x27;s Liberation Front and fight against the Derg (the Mengistu Haile Mariam-led military government in Ethiopia).

